File: A security guard has been shot during an alleged robbery at Cresta mall in Randburg on Tuesday. JOHANNESBURG - A security guard has been shot during an alleged robbery at Cresta mall in Randburg on Tuesday. ER24 says a man, believed to be in his 30s, was left seriously injured after he was shot on the leg. The man was reportedly treated at a clinic at the mall before being taken to a private hospital. Local authorities were reportedly on the scene. More to follow